	   <tr><td colspan=2>Anywhere you have nothing, get some cured silk.  That should be top priority and it won't cost that much.  Don't pay more than 2-3 pp per ac.  You need some magic gloves.  Wu's are nothing special but you can kill wisps and other magic only mobs with them.  Don't pay more than 50 pp.  Orc fang earrings have gotten cheap.  Jagged bands are very nice, and about 50-60 pp.  You can't afford all of these with your 150 p - get what you can find - get the CS first.  Lightweight AC is top priority.<br><br>Hope this helps<br><br>Keyeluke<br>Monk of the Silent Fist<br>Strange Brew<br>Druzzil Ro<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
