	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have to disagree, albeit slightly.  Here's how the numbers work out at lvl 35:<br><br>Baton/Baton  9.14 hp/sec<br>Baton/CoT    9.44<br>CoT/CoT      9.60<br><br>Two CoTs outdamage two batons by 6%.  Not a big difference, but it's there.  Does it justify the cost difference?  Depends how rich you are.  Plus, there's something to be said for having a faster primary (baton) to help interrupt casters.<br><br>Also, a Wu's stick performs more poorly in the off hand than either a baton or a CoT.  There are a lot of choices for off hand, but by and large the tables suggest you want a high damage off hand and a fast primary.  Knuckle dusters seem to be the best off hand that is not impossible to acquire.<br><br>Jade Mace and KD is where I want to get to, at least until I can do Celestial Fists ;)<br><br>Keyeluke<br>Monk of the Silent Fist<br>Strange Brew<br>Druzzil Ro<br><br>Here's the link with the data:<br><br><a href="http://tinaddar.kung-foo.org/monk1hb.html" target=_new>http://tinaddar.kung-foo.org/monk1hb.html</a><br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
