	   <tr><td colspan=2>It matters a great deal.  Expect to lose 4 points of AC for every pound (or stone or unit) over 14.  The penalty per pound decreases as you get really heavy, but by then your AC is in the toilet.  Unfortunately, it's a penalty that's tough to avoid all the time, and pretty much impossible to avoid if you're going to carry a 2HB around to practice with.  Best bet, practice up your 2HB to its max at your level, then bank it till you ding again.  If you can, choose zones near banks.  When you get a little higher level, High Pass Hold and High Keep are awesome monk zones, because the High Keep bank is so close by.<br><br><br>Keyeluke<br>Monk of the Silent Fist<br>Strange Brew<br>Druzzil Ro<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
	   </form></table><ul>

</ul>

</ul>
