	   <tr><td colspan=2>Right now, my Iksar Monk is lvl 20 and has a Master Wu's Trance Stick and a Knuckle Duster(this is my main).  I saw another monk with two Wu's Trance Stick and asked her if she liked it. She said they were better than what i have, but i wasn't sure if she was right.  Which combo is better: two Wu's Trance Sticks or a Wu's Trance Stick and a Knuckle Dusters and why?  FYI: Wu's Trance Stick is 7/18 Effect-Smite_procs at lvl 35; Knuckle Dusters are 14/28.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
